---
layout: "base-layout.njk"
title: "Our Services: Crafting Your Ideal Space"
description: "We offer a comprehensive range of interior design services, from residential and commercial design to space planning and project management, meticulously crafted to bring your vision to life."
---

<header class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
        <p class="page-intro">We offer a comprehensive range of interior design services, meticulously crafted to meet your unique needs and bring your design aspirations to fruition.</p>
    </div>
</header>

<section class="services-main">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="service-grid">
            {% for service in services_dummy %}
            <div class="service-card">
                {% if service.image %}
                <div class="service-card__image-wrapper">
                    <img src="{{ service.image }}" alt="{{ service.title }}" class="service-card__image" loading="lazy">
                </div>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="service-card__content">
                    <h2 class="service-card__title">{{ service.title }}</h2>
                    <p class="service-card__description">{{ service.intro }}</p>
                    <div class="service-card__meta">
                        <div class="meta-item">
                            <span class="meta-item__label">Investment</span>
                            <span class="meta-item__value">{{ service.investment.split('.')[0] }}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/services/{{ service.slug }}/" class="button button--secondary service-card__cta">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>

        <div class="faq-prompt">
            <p>Have questions about timelines, budgets, or our process? <a href="/about#faq">Visit our FAQ page for answers</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>